d52952
iIn a bowl, add the beef, salt, 1 pinch white pepper, 1 Teaspoon sesame seed oil, 1/2 egg, corn starch,1 Tablespoon of oil and mix together.
iIn a 6 qt pot add your noodles to boiling water until the noodles are submerged and boil on high heat for 10 seconds.
iAfter your noodles is done boiling strain and cool with cold water.
iAdd 2 Tablespoons of oil, beef and cook on high heat untill beef is medium cooked.
