nCorned Beef and Cabbage
cBeef
d52998
iPlace corned beef in large pot or Dutch oven and cover with water.
iAdd the spice packet that came with the corned beef.
iCover pot and bring to a boil, then reduce to a simmer.
iSimmer approximately 50 minutes per pound or until tender.
iAdd whole potatoes and peeled and cut carrots, and cook until the vegetables are almost tender.
iAdd cabbage and cook for 15 more minutes.
iRemove meat and let rest 15 minutes.
iPlace vegetables in a bowl and cover.
iAdd as much broth (cooking liquid reserved in the Dutch oven or large pot) as you want.
iSlice meat across the grain.
