iBring a large amount of water to a boil and then add a pinch of salt.
iSlide the tofu in and cook for 1 minute.
iMove out and drain.
iGet a wok and heat up around 2 tablespoons of oil, fry the minced meat until crispy.
iTransfer out beef out and leave the oil in.
