nBrown Stew Chicken
cChicken
d52940
iSqueeze lime over chicken and rub well.
iDrain off excess lime juice.
iCombine tomato, scallion, onion, garlic, pepper, thyme, pimento and soy sauce in a large bowl with the chicken pieces.
iCover and marinate at least one hour.
iHeat oil in a dutch pot or large saucepan.
iShake off the seasonings as you remove each piece of chicken from the marinade.
iReserve the marinade for sauce.
