nKatsu Chicken curry
cChicken
d52820
iFor the curry sauce: Heat oil in medium non-stick saucepan, add onion and garlic and cook until softened.
iStir in carrots and cook over low heat for 10 to 12 minutes.
iAdd flour and curry powder; cook for 1 minute.
iGradually stir in stock until combined; add honey, soy sauce and bay leaf.
iSlowly bring to the boil.
iTurn down heat and simmer for 20 minutes or until sauce thickens but is still of pouring consistency.
iStir in garam masala.
