nTandoori chicken
cChicken
d52806
iMix the lemon juice with the paprika and red onions in a large shallow dish.
iSlash each chicken thigh three times, then turn them in the juice and set aside for 10 mins.
iMix all of the marinade ingredients together and pour over the chicken.
iGive everything a good mix, then cover and chill for at least 1 hr.
iThis can be done up to a day in advance.
iHeat the grill.
iLift the chicken pieces onto a rack over a baking tray.
iBrush over a little oil and grill for 8 mins on each side or until lightly charred and completely cooked through.
