d52854
iPut the flour, eggs, milk, 1 tbsp oil and a pinch of salt into a bowl or large jug, then whisk to a smooth batter.
iSet aside for 30 mins to rest if you have time, or start cooking straight away.
iSet a medium frying pan or crêpe pan over a medium heat and carefully wipe it with some oiled kitchen paper.
