nParkin Cake
cDessert
d52902
iHeat oven to 160C/140C fan/gas 3.
iGrease a deep 22cm/9in square cake tin and line with baking parchment.
iBeat the egg and milk together with a fork.
iGently melt the syrup, treacle, sugar and butter together in a large pan until the sugar has dissolved.
iRemove from the heat.
