iHeat oven to 190C/170C fan/gas 5.
iButter a wide shallow ovenproof dish.
iBlend the cornflour with the orange zest and juice, and put in a large pan with the sugar.
iHalve, stone and slice the peaches and add to the pan.
iBring slowly to the boil, stirring gently until the sauce is shiny and thickened, about 3-4 mins.
