d52804
iHeat oil in a deep fryer or deep heavy skillet to 365°F (185°C).
iWarm gravy in saucepan or microwave.
iPlace the fries into the hot oil, and cook until light brown, about 5 minutes.
iRemove to a paper towel lined plate to drain.
iPlace the fries on a serving platter, and sprinkle the cheese over them.
iLadle gravy over the fries and cheese, and serve immediately.
