nMatar Paneer
cVegetarian
d52865
iHeat the oil in a frying pan over high heat until it’s shimmering hot.
iAdd the paneer, then turn the heat down a little.
iFry until it starts to brown at the edges, then turn it over and brown on each side – the paneer will brown faster than you think, so don’t walk away.
iRemove the paneer from the pan and drain on kitchen paper.
iPut the ginger, cumin, turmeric, ground coriander and chilli in the pan, and fry everything for 1 min.
